title: ‘Survivor,’ Season 42, Episode 6 With Kim Spradlin-Wolfe
description:
Riley and Juliet are joined by ‘Survivor: One World’ winner and ‘Survivor: Winners at War’ contestant Kim Spradlin-Wolfe. They discuss the drama leading up to the “pre-merge” and break down another chaotic Tribal Council vote.
Hosts: Riley McAtee and Juliet Litman
Guest: Kim Spradlin-Wolfe
Production: Carlos Chiriboga
